                    <section>
                        <p class="mb-4">Ginkgo Health Inc. (“Ginkgo Health”, “Ginkgo” “we”, “us” or “our”) provides digital healthcare content, functionality and other products and services to you when you visit <a href="http://www.ginkgo.health" class="text-emerald-600 hover:underline">www.ginkgo.health</a> (the “Website”) or use the Ginkgo mobile application (the “App”) (collectively, the “Service”).</p>
                        <p>Ginkgo is committed to protecting and respecting your privacy through our compliance with PIPEDA. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, protect and share information about you, as an individual, that we obtain when you access and use the Service.</p>
