                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-stone-800 mb-2">Technical Information from Your Use of the Service</h3>
                        <p class="mb-3">We also collect and store certain technical information when you access, browse and use the Service. This technical information helps us operate the Service and provide access to you, and includes standard information about visits and system capabilities, such as:</p>
                        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 mb-4 text-stone-700">
